"Under control. If I return to it & it's not... then it will NOT be a pretty 
sight." she stated with a little threatening voice. 

"Once we get the Decepticons, we need to return immediately to Predacon Base. 
Hopefully, Hydras has come out of stasis lock & repaired. I need to speak 
with him." More about some issues & current events that she doubted he would like 
at all.
